displayName: Para Village - Home of Alchemist Miti

parameters: Alchemist Miti: ...Please don't disturb my research.
Clea: I checked the notice board in Oros.

Alchemist Miti: Ah... I can't shake off this gloomy
feeling, but if you all came, then it should be fine.

Alchemist Miti: I want you to find the Eyes of Oradoru in
my place.

Mage Relm: What do you plan to use the Eyes of Oradoru
for!?
Clea: Is it really that dangerous?

Mage Relm: While it is a herb that can be used to enhance
the body, if the dosage is incorrect, it can become a deadly
poison for the body.
Mage Relm: You don't mean to commit suicide...!

Alchemist Miti: As a researcher myself, if I were to die, I
would prefer to do so in a more rational manner.

Alchemist Miti: In my research, I believe that a small
amount of intake can improve one's mental state.
Clea: Understood, I will go and obtain it.

Alchemist Miti: I don't doubt that you will bring the real
thing, but previously I was given some random weeds...
Alchemist Miti: ...I believe in all of you.
Clea: I have brought the Orb of Ador.

Alchemist Miti: Thank goodness... I'll mix it right away
and try drinking it.

Alchemist Miti: I-I'm starting to feel a bit
lightheaded...

Clea: I will stay here. Everyone, please wait outside, it's
okay.
Mage Relm: I don't think Clea-san needs to go that far.

Clea: I haven't received the reward yet, and I've heard
that it's a dangerous herb.
Mage Relm: Understood, we will rest in the village then.
Alchemist Miti: Ah, it's the best... the absolute best...

Alchemist Miti: I'm so frustrated! It's not working at all!
This is a fake!

Clea: P-Please calm down. This is the genuine article that
we obtained in the Valt region!

Alchemist Miti: How can I stay calm when I've been deceived
with a fake!
Clea (She seems clearly strange... What on earth is this?)

Alchemist Miti: If you claim it's genuine, then you should
be able to drink it right in front of me!
Alchemist Miti: Come on! Come on, drink it!
Alchemist Miti: Hah... What on earth...

Clea: It seems like you were temporarily confused due to
the medicine, but if you have returned to your senses, then
there's no problem.

Alchemist Miti: There's an issue with the amount... No, the
problem lies in the extraction method...

Alchemist Miti: I'll pay you the reward later for your
research. Can you also accept a nuisance fee?
Clea: Thank you very much, then.

Alchemist Miti: If you're willing, I'd like you to continue
assisting with my research. Your strength seems sufficient
to handle even my outbursts, so it should be fine.

Clea: I understand... If you doubt it that much, then I
will drink it.

Clea: (This is the effect of body enhancement... No... This
feeling... Rather...)
Clea (M-My body... it feels like it's... in heat!)

Alchemist Miti: Has the effect kicked in...? Let me confirm
it.
Would you like to skip the adult scene?

Alchemist Miti: What have I done...! I'm truly, truly
sorry...!

Clea: No... If you could just forget about it, it'll be
fine.
Clea: And please give me my reward as well.

Alchemist Miti: I'm sorry... I want you to accept the
reward and apology.

Alchemist Miti: If it's alright with you, would you help me
with my research again?
Clea: I'll think about it. Well then, that's all.

Alchemist Miti: If you drink the medicine, your mood will
improve, but if you don't drink it, your mood will plummet
to the depths of despair...

events.name: 疑心暗鬼な錬金術士自動実行

parameters: Do you want to skip the adult scene?

Alchemist Miti: It seems like you drank it properly! Now,
I'll make sure to confirm if the delivered medicinal herbs
are genuine!

Alchemist Miti: Show it to me carefully! I want you to
accompany me in my research!
